<p>真的好不容易才裝成功…</p>

<p>安裝指令如下:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">sudo </span>dpkg <span class="nt">--add-architecture</span> i386

<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt update

<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install </span>gdebi wget gdebi-core libgl1-mesa-glx:i386

wget <span class="nt">-O</span> ~/steam.deb http://media.steampowered.com/client/installer/steam.deb

<span class="nb">sudo </span>gdebi ~/steam.deb</code></pre></figure>

